      • select

        Iterator select(Class selectClass,
                String queryWhere,
                Object[] params,
                String queryOrder,
                OAObject whereObject,
                String propertyFromWhereObject,
                String extraWhere,
                int max,
                OAFilter filter,
                boolean bDirty)
        Parameters:
        selectClass -
        queryWhere - where clause for selecting objects.
        params - param values for "?" in the queryWhere.
        queryOrder - sort order
        whereObject - master object to select from.
        propertyFromWhereObject -
        extraWhere - added to the query.
        max -
        filter - this can be used if the datasource does not support a way to query for the results.
        bDirty - true if objects should be fully populated, even if they are already loaded (in cache, etc).
        Returns:
